Marcus Toji https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcus_Toji 0 Marcus Mamoru Toji is an American actor and voice actor best known for his role on Movie Surfers. Born in California in 1984, Toji attended Beverly Hills High School, was in a Betty Crocker Commercial for fruit snacks and won a Copper Wing Award in 2006 for his role in movie Self Medicated.
